data.description: An exciting lifestyle where location is key awaits in this light-filled upgraded residence in desirable Woodland Hills displaying a new roof energy efficient windows, and a custom stone terrace. Enjoy 3 levels of living spaces in this townhome featuring impeccable interiors, new hardwoods, a foyer entry leading to a family room and stairs to the next level. Boasting natural light, this home presents a bright living room enhanced by a glass slider opening to the deck and an ambient fireplace, a dining room adjacent to the kitchen with a box bay window, and well-appointed kitchen. Epicurean by design, the kitchen showcases a center island with pendant lighting and a breakfast bar, stainless steel appliances, Shaker style cabinetry, newly installed quartz counters with harmonizing tile backsplash, and a box bay window casual dining space. Spacious owner’s suite is highlighted by a vaulted ceiling with a drop ceiling fan, a walk-in closet, and a private bath displaying a shower with tile inlays and a relaxing jetted tub. Nicely finished lower level offers a rec room, a full bath, and extra storage. Amazing location in close proximity to shopping, recreation, Lake Whetstone, Shady Grove Metro and major commuter routes. eligible for our MMCT (majority minority census tract) program.
